    "profileHelpVendorsSection": "VENDORS",
    "profileHelpBookingQuestion1": "How do I book a vendor?",
    "profileHelpBookingQuestion2": "Can I cancel or reschedule a booking?",
    "profileHelpBookingQuestion3": "What payment methods are accepted?",
    "profileHelpBookingAnswer1": "Browse vendor profiles, compare packages, pick your preferred date, and submit a booking request. You will receive a confirmation once the vendor accepts and payment is completed.",
    "profileHelpBookingAnswer2": "Yes. Open the booking details page and send a cancellation or reschedule request before the vendor's cutoff time. Approval depends on the vendor's policy and event timeline.",
    "profileHelpBookingAnswer3": "Eventra supports card payments, bank transfer options, and any other payment methods clearly listed by the vendor during checkout.",
    "profileHelpAccountQuestion1": "How do I reset my password?",
    "profileHelpAccountQuestion2": "How do I update my profile information?",
    "profileHelpAccountQuestion3": "Can I have multiple addresses?",
    "profileHelpAccountAnswer1": "Go to Privacy & Security, select update password, and enter your current and new password. If you are logged out, use the forgot password flow from the sign-in page.",
    "profileHelpAccountAnswer2": "Open your profile settings to update details like your name, contact information, and preferences. Save changes to refresh your account information immediately.",
    "profileHelpAccountAnswer3": "Yes. You can save multiple addresses and choose the most relevant one during checkout or event planning whenever that option is available.",
    "profileHelpPaymentsQuestion1": "When will I be charged?",
    "profileHelpPaymentsQuestion2": "Are there any additional fees?",
    "profileHelpPaymentsQuestion3": "How do refunds work?",
    "profileHelpPaymentsAnswer1": "You are charged when you confirm a booking and complete payment. Some vendors may require a deposit first, with the balance settled later based on their terms.",
    "profileHelpPaymentsAnswer2": "Any service fees, taxes, or vendor-specific charges are shown clearly before you confirm payment so there are no hidden surprises.",
    "profileHelpPaymentsAnswer3": "Refund timelines depend on the vendor's cancellation policy. When approved, refunds are processed back to your original payment method within the stated review window.",
    "profileHelpVendorsQuestion1": "How are vendors verified?",
    "profileHelpVendorsQuestion2": "Can I message vendors before booking?",
    "profileHelpVendorsQuestion3": "What if I have issues with a vendor?",
